- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is another possible category as the paper mentions the role of parity automata in game theory. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper discusses algorithms for determinisation. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is the least likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with formal languages and automata theory, which are relevant to programming language theory.
